      <title>海地在持续动荡中更换总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/haiti-replaces-its-prime-minister-amid-continued-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地报纸《海地公报》报道，海地过渡总统委员会任命阿利克斯·迪迪埃·菲尔斯·艾梅为这个陷入困境的加勒比国家的新任总理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/haiti-replaces-its-prime-minister-amid-continued-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 22:27:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨为圣诞节前举行德国信任投票打开大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/scholz-says-confidence-vote-would-be-possible-before-christmas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨表示，他愿意将议会信任投票提前数周至圣诞节前举行，这可能会将德国大选提前至 2 月份举行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/scholz-says-confidence-vote-would-be-possible-before-christmas</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 21:36:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部长警告称，特朗普胜选将给澳大利亚带来经济损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/australia-faces-economic-pain-from-trump-win-treasurer-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚财政部长吉姆·查尔默斯表示，受美国新任总统唐纳德·特朗普的政策议程影响，澳大利亚面临产出下降和通胀压力进一步加大等短期经济痛苦的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/australia-faces-economic-pain-from-trump-win-treasurer-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 21:11:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索马里内阁支持前陆军参谋长回国任职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/somali-cabinet-backs-former-army-chief-for-return-stint-at-helm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在摩加迪沙内阁部长召开的特别会议上，索马里国民军前司令奥达瓦·尤素夫·拉吉被提名重返该职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/somali-cabinet-backs-former-army-chief-for-return-stint-at-helm</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 20:52:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称参议院下一任领导人必须支持休会期间任命</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/donald-trump-says-senate-s-next-leader-must-favor-recess-appointments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普参与了美国参议院下一任多数党领袖的竞选，他表示，任何竞选该职位的共和党人都必须支持休会期间任命，以便新政府的职位能够“及时”填补。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/donald-trump-says-senate-s-next-leader-must-favor-recess-appointments</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 20:20:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《华盛顿邮报》称特朗普建议普京不要让乌克兰局势升级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/trump-advised-putin-against-ukraine-upturn-washington-post-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《华盛顿邮报》周日报道，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普建议俄罗斯总统普京不要升级乌克兰战争，并提醒他美国在欧洲拥有庞大的军事存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/trump-advised-putin-against-ukraine-upturn-washington-post-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 20:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>威尔伯·罗斯称特朗普可能会免除加拿大能源关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/trump-is-likely-to-exempt-canadian-energy-from-tariffs-wilbur-ross-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前商务部长威尔伯·罗斯表示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将贯彻对进口产品征收关税的计划，但可能会为加拿大石油和天然气等行业提供豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/trump-is-likely-to-exempt-canadian-energy-from-tariffs-wilbur-ross-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 19:38:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>做空特斯拉的对冲基金刚刚损失了 50 多亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/hedge-funds-shorting-tesla-just-lost-more-than-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自唐纳德·特朗普赢得大选以来，那些坚持做空特斯拉公司的对冲基金已经损失了数十亿美元，因为他们感受到了候任总统和埃隆·马斯克之间特殊关系的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/hedge-funds-shorting-tesla-just-lost-more-than-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通为特朗普执政头两年“影响深远”做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/jpmorgan-braces-for-impactful-first-two-years-of-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通私人银行董事总经理斯蒂芬·格拉泽 (Stefan Gratzer) 表示，如果在税收、放松管制和加密货币方面做出政策变化，唐纳德·特朗普第二任期的头两年可能会“颇具影响力”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/jpmorgan-braces-for-impactful-first-two-years-of-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 17:52:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国财长默茨希望与特朗普达成协议，称肖尔茨是“跛脚鸭”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/germany-s-merz-open-for-deals-with-trump-calls-scholz-lame-duck</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国反对党领袖弗里德里希·梅尔茨在预计的提前选举前的民意调查中占据主导地位，他表示将寻求与即将上任的美国总统唐纳德·特朗普签署协议，以提升德国的国际地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/germany-s-merz-open-for-deals-with-trump-calls-scholz-lame-duck</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 11:47:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
